title: Tyron Woodley vs. Jake Paul: who really won?

UFC Legend and Jake Paul’s worst nightmare Tyron Woodley joins us just 3 days before his highly anticipated fight with Jake Paul. Is he ready? What will happen? The world is watching and the anticipation is killing us!!
